.toCharArray() = it convert String into character array And Return type char[]
Character.isLetter('charchater') = check wheather mentioned character is letter or not and return boolean value
Character.isDigit(numeric value) = check wheather mentioned character is integer(digit) or not and return boolean value
Character.isSpaceChar( _ (Space)) = check wheather mentioned character is Space or not and return boolean value
Arrays.toString(Array list) = mentioned Array list convert into String data type Array
Arrays.sort(Array list) = mentioned array list sorted Acesending order but arrays list data type must be String 